### Lancer le calcul carbone pour un site
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sites/7/calcul
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Historique des calculs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sites/3/historique
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### KPIs du dernier calcul
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sites/1/kpis
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Creer un site complet avec employes et transports
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Bureau Paris",
  "adresse": "12 rue de la Paix",
  "ville": "Paris",
  "surfaceTotale": 5000,
  "nbPlaces": 100,
  "typeBatiment": "BUREAU",
  "dureeVie": 50,
  "eElec": 800000,
  "eGaz": 400000,
  "nombreEmployes": 500,
  "nombrePostesTravail": 350,
  "materiaux": [
    { "materiauId": 1, "quantite": 4000 },
    { "materiauId": 2, "quantite": 250 },
    { "materiauId": 3, "quantite": 100 },
    { "materiauId": 4, "quantite": 80 }
  ],
  "employes": [
    {
      "nb": 300,
      "modeTravail": "SUR_SITE",
      "transports": [
        { "mode": "VOITURE_THERMIQUE", "distance": 15 },
        { "mode": "METRO", "distance": 8 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "nb": 150,
      "modeTravail": "HYBRIDE",
      "joursSite": 114,
      "transports": [
        { "mode": "TRAIN", "distance": 25 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "nb": 50,
      "modeTravail": "REMOTE"
    }
  ]
}
